Twitter was ablaze after reports emerged that Amazon founder Jeff Bezos could become the world's first trillionaire. According to a Comparisun report, the world's richest net worth has grown by 34% on average over the last five years. This could potentially see him become the world’s first trillionaire as early as 2026. At 2026, he’ll be aged 62. Twitter users were angry as the Covid-19 pandemic was thrust in the spotlight as well as the alleged mistreatment of Amazon workers.     IOL TECH